<Content_wSideColumn ID="x18695" Name="Checklist" Layout="byuidefault.xsl"><Title type="string" label="Title" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">The Graduation Checklist</Title><Abstract type="string" label="Abstract" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="true">Grad Check List</Abstract><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="SideColumn" label="L/R Column" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><MoveLeft type="boolean" label="Toggle column right or left (right is default)" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</MoveLeft><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="ImageComponent" label="Image Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="LeftColumnImageComponent" Expanded="false"/><xPower Type="Component" Component="" Name="TextComponent" label="Text Component" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="ColumnTextComponent" Expanded="false"/><fbookTop type="boolean" label="Put facebook at top of page" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">false</fbookTop><fbookStatus type="string" label="Facebook ID#" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"></fbookStatus><fbookDisplayed type="string" label="Number of facebook messages to display" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false">1</fbookDisplayed></xPower><BodyCopy type="dhtml" label="Body Copy" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<div><!--                Graduation Check List                  --> 
<ul>
<li style="text-align: left;">At least 1-2 semesters prior to graduation meet with your <a href="http://igx.byui.edu/advising/Career_And_Academic_Advising.html" style="color: #38acec;">satellite academic discovery center</a> to ensure you will complete all degree requirements.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Determine whether or not you will be marching at Commencement and/or in your college Convocation. You will need to know this as part of the graduation application process. </li>
<li style="text-align: left;">If marching, determine if you need to purchase a cap and gown. You will also need this information for the graduation application process.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;"><a href="https://my.byui.edu/ICS/Academics/" style="color: #38acec;">Apply for graduation</a></li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Watch your BYU-I email account for important, specific information regarding graduation events.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Order graduation <a href="http://www.byuistore.com/c-74-grad-announcements.aspx" style="color: #38acec;">announcements and other memorabilia</a>.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Plan to attend <a href="http://www.byuiconnect.org" style="color: #38acec;">Grad Night</a> during the semester you will graduate.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Plan to attend <a href="http://www.byuiconnect.org" style="color: #38acec;">Grad Fest </a>during the semester you will graduate to pick up your cap, gown, and name card.</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Pick up Commencement tickets at the <a href="http://www.byui.edu/tickets/" style="color: #38acec;">Ticket Office</a> for your family and guests. (Tickets are not required for Convocation.)</li>
<li style="text-align: left;">Determine the location, date, and time of your college's <a href="x18323.xml" style="color: #38acec;">Convocation</a>.</li>
<li>Inform your family and guests of the dates and times of graduation events. Remind them to be seated at least 30 minutes prior to start of Commencement.</li>
<li>Attend your individual college's Convocation to receive your Diploma cover. If you are not participating in Convocation, visit the Student Records and Registration office (Kim 190) to pick up a diploma cover prior to leaving campus.</li>
</ul>
